  "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "In lieu of `send()`'s 2300 gas stipend changing [EIP1884](https://eips.ethereum.org/EIPS/eip-1884) we need to provide:\r\n\r\na.) Docs for the possibity of `send()` causing trouble in future forks.\r\nb.) Non-`rawcall` based method of doing .call() and add recommendation for using `@nonreentrant()` alongside it in the docs.\r\n\r\nLinks\r\n- https://diligence.consensys.net/posts/2019/09/stop-using-soliditys-transfer-now/",
