    "body": "As suggesed on gitter (cc @smarx) we might look at creating a function such as:\r\n```python\r\ncall_default(self.token_address, value=as_wei_value(1, \"ether\"))\r\n```\r\nWhich would be the equivalent of\r\n```python\r\nraw_call(self, b\"\", outsize=0, value=as_wei_value(1, \"ether\"), gas=msg.gas)\r\n```\r\nWhich is more vyper-like.",
